headline.print_headline: Japan PM Abe Wants to Confirm Further Cooperation With Australia
headline.main: Japan PM Abe Wants to Confirm Further Cooperation With Australia

lead_paragraph: Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe said on Monday he wants to confirm further cooperation on defense and the economy with Australian premier Tony Abbott, who is visiting Tokyo.
